            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription" ana="b1">
                <p>
               <choice>
                        <orig>Μνημῖον</orig>
                        <reg>μνημεῖον</reg>
                    </choice> Σούμμου<lb/>Ὀλέφου, ἀποθανόν<lb break="no"/>τος ἐτῶν <num value="42">μβ</num>
                    <choice>
                        <orig>ἐν ἔτι</orig>
                        <reg>ἐν ἔτει</reg>
                    </choice>
               <lb/>
               <num value="314">τιδ</num>, μηνὸς <choice>
                        <orig>Πανέ<lb break="no"/>μου</orig>
                        <reg>Πανήμου</reg>
                    </choice>
                    <num value="26">κς</num>, <choice>
                        <orig>τελευτέ<lb break="no"/>σαντος</orig>
                        <reg>τελευτήσαντος</reg>
                    </choice> μετὰ κα<lb break="no"/>λοῦ ὀνόματος. <lb/>
               <choice>
                        <orig>Θάρσι</orig>
                        <orig>θάρσει</orig>
                    </choice>
                    <choice>
                        <orig>οὐδὶς</orig>
                        <reg>οὐδείς</reg>
                    </choice> ἀθάνα<lb break="no"/>τος. Ἡμέρᾳ Κυρίου <num value="3">γ</num>.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>Monument of Summus, (son) of Olefos, who died (at the age) of 42 years, in the
                    year 314, on the 26th (day) of (the) month Panemos; he passed away having a good
                    name. Be of good cheer, no one (is) immortal. (He died) on the 3rd day of (the)
                    Lord (Tuesday).</p>
            </div>
